<h2 id="常见问题与误区">常见问题与误区</h2>
<h3 id="问题1embedding模型与业务场景不匹配">问题1：Embedding模型与业务场景不匹配</h3>
<p><strong>根因</strong>：通用Embedding在垂直领域语义捕捉不准确
<strong>解决</strong>：使用领域特化模型，或对通用模型做微调</p>]]></description></item><item><title>RAG与向量检索</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E4%B8%8E%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90/rag%E4%B8%8E%E5%90%91%E9%87%8F%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E4%B8%8E%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90/rag%E4%B8%8E%E5%90%91%E9%87%8F%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="rag与向量检索">RAG与向量检索</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：RAG通过向量检索获取相关知识再生成回答，解决了大模型幻觉和知识时效问题，向量检索的核心是Embedding模型将文本转为高维向量，通过ANN算法在毫秒级找到最近邻。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="rag通过向量检索获取上下文再生成embeddingann是语义搜索的核心技术栈">RAG通过向量检索获取上下文再生成，Embedding+ANN是语义搜索的核心技术栈</h2>
<h3 id="rag架构检索增强生成">RAG架构：检索增强生成</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">用户提问: &#34;公司的年假政策是什么？&#34;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Embedding模型 → 将问题转为向量 Query-Vector
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">向量数据库检索 → 找出Top-K相似的文档片段
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">构建Prompt: 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  &#34;基于以下信息回答问题：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   [文档片段1] [文档片段2] [文档片段3]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   问题：公司的年假政策是什么？&#34;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">LLM生成回答</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>RAG vs 微调</strong>：</p>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>维度</th>
